hopobject.body: Which year are you in? r-pharm pipeline At approximately 9.10pm the pie came out of the oven and dinner was served. The pie had no soggy bottom, although with the amount of pastry present, I had never really feared any drop of moisture would get through that cement-like case, and the layers of vegetables and cheese were visible - sort of. Cutting a slice was quite tricky as the sides collapsed a bit – but other than that it looked good and my flatmate really enjoyed it.
